---
title: Tofu and Braised Cabbage with Horseradish Smashed Potatoes
description: The chilly evenings have us craving dishes that'll warm us inside and out. With fragrant, roasted tofu served atop braised red cabbage and apple, plus a pile of creamy mashed potatoes alongside, this comforting dish does exactly that!
